Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏天到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到夏天就是海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到海就是泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样 每年为了万一的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.03,0:01:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而准备胜负泳衣 这是女孩子的常识啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样信以为真是不行的 葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么就出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.24,0:01:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有可爱的泳装就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.37,0:01:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得好兴奋呢 雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.61,0:01:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泳装我就不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？为什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.49,0:02:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.93,0:02:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十六话  渚（海边）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要什么样的泳装才能让花菱少爷喜悦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个也难以割舍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.25,0:02:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像您这么美丽的客人 这件比较适合喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.25,0:02:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.06,0:02:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子我就能完美的得到花菱少爷的心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 这是多么棒的设计啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.13,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样简单的设计 把我的美丽给衬托出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对 为什么是学校的泳衣啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好 繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭也是来买泳装的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很适合你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的眼光真不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给小鬼头穿刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 能不能请你不要防碍我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊 难得我想帮你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你多管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会给其他客人带来困扰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你们大家一起试穿的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样？看这大人的魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样海边的女主角就决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样子太低俗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比较起来我会以这份优雅独占海边所有的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子很帅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这样很可爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子很性感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这样子当然比较好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？只有这件吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.60,0:04:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常对不起 客人您的尺寸有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是非常适合您喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.65,0:04:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟您一起去海边的男性一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么是学长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行不行不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这样的啦 好丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能跟薰两个人一起去一定很快乐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏天果然就是要玩破西瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样 还是我的最合适吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是我的比较好吧 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 为什么连我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 大家都很合适啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 水无月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到一张你外婆寄过来的明信片喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外婆寄过来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会适合…我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海边耶 房东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.41,0:05:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海边耶 海边海边海边海边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.45,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 小葵 其实啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙的外婆寄来了一张明信片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 好漂亮的地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我外婆经营的『海之家』那边的海边喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.44,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海之家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后…外婆她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（给妙子 今年也来玩吧 外婆上）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海边 海边 海边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一点都安静不下来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿成那样有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是…真不知道高兴的是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧 管理员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理员？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.76,0:06:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对啊 哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是来对了呢 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.46,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想你喔 妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是一样有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.46,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有稍微长高一点了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这一年可是长高了五公分喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来介绍 这女孩是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是她表妹水无月千夏 请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多指教 千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个人是妙姐姐的男朋友对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千千千千夏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰是…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 学长是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这女孩子说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷是我最重要的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐的男朋友真是受欢迎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你说不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.84,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎远道而来 小妙变的很像外国人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然女孩子一久没见就变很多了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外婆 我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.19,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年带了这么多朋友来 会很热闹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 连老公也一起带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 来海边玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷要跟我一起玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以不用帮忙了 你也去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然都带了朋友来 就好好享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 妙姐姐 一起来玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 快一点 快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 讨厌 不要拉我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很高兴吧 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能呼吸啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还想再飞一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.41,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷 我的脚抽筋了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 小繭 脚不要贴上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们要干嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦 好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要防碍我的夏季恋曲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么夏季恋曲啊 你这个乳臭未干的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦 好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么啊？夏天的回忆就是要大胆一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像变成非常激烈的争吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐不能输给她们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没关系的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么啊 男朋友会被抢走喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说你搞错了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦 快过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.38,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了 我要死了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 妙姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一个人来的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.04,0:10:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要跟我们一起玩啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？啊…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦 好啦 一起走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？啊！那个我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.55,0:10:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐又被男人搭讪了 能好好拒绝就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我带飞盘来了 一起来玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊 有带男人来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.61,0:10:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找下一个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 一起来玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏也一起来玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.86,0:11:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.73,0:11:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐这样子真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易跟薰少爷一起来到海边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.07,0:11:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没关系的…因为我也没有带泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对雅说谎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.53,0:11:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在大家面前穿泳装 我果然还是会害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下 葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们两个人一起来享受夏天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 我的夏天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.02,0:12:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能够像那个样子自然的玩就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.69,0:12:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧 钿女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡着了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.53,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.86,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吓一跳了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你一个人在发呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.00,0:12:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 真是没用对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.91,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畏畏缩缩的不肯表达自己的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旁边看的人都快急死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.28,0:12:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙姐姐她从以前开始一点都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在说妙子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.52,0:12:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不再更积极一点是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.39,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不这样的话 就抓不住喜欢的人的心了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这杂志上都有写啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何要好好谈个恋爱才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请拿去 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起啊 都是因为蒂娜她使劲全力丢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵你不去游泳吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为露给别人看实在是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是有点可惜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵穿泳装的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要好好谈个恋爱才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 别想落跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我一起火辣和热情的夏季恋曲 现在才要开始喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不是那样的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让你跑掉的…我的夏天！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.99,0:14:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（民宿 涟漪）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.16,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴巴张开 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用啦 我自己会吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.13,0:14:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 别光只是吃 再多喝一点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边的酒可是很棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来一碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？已经第四碗了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿 因为跟大家一起吃饭很好吃嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙子 也麻烦你再帮我添一碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.89,0:14:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去 学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.73,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙 这样会吃坏肚子的啦
